{
  "video_id": "YeYW8TIWLG8",
  "title": "Computer Simulation (Pixar in a Box)",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 742.0,
      "end_time": 2027.0,
      "text": "Hi, I'm Hayley Iben"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2027.0000000000002,
      "end_time": 3993.0,
      "text": "I'm a software engineer at Pixar."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 3993.0,
      "end_time": 5527.0,
      "text": "I worked on the hair simulator"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 5527.0,
      "end_time": 7516.0,
      "text": "for the movie, Brave."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 7516.0,
      "end_time": 9752.0,
      "text": "Hair was a really big deal in Brave."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 9752.0,
      "end_time": 11518.0,
      "text": "It was a symbol of freedom that was intrinsic"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 11518.0,
      "end_time": 14514.0,
      "text": "to our main character Merida's personality."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 14514.0,
      "end_time": 16297.0,
      "text": "And making hair that feels right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 16297.0,
      "end_time": 18246.0,
      "text": "meaning messy, wild and free,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 18246.0,
      "end_time": 21013.0,
      "text": "is a hard thing to do computationally."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 21013.0,
      "end_time": 23501.0,
      "text": "In our movies, hair is a simulated effect."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 23501.0,
      "end_time": 26248.0,
      "text": "That means no one animates its movement by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 26248.0,
      "end_time": 28031.0,
      "text": "The way it moves is defined by physics"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 28031.0,
      "end_time": 30314.0,
      "text": "and programmed into the computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 30314.0,
      "end_time": 32535.0,
      "text": "To figure out what hair simulation should look like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 32534.999999999996,
      "end_time": 34240.0,
      "text": "we needed to look at real curly hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 35741.0,
      "text": "and see how it worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 35741.0,
      "end_time": 37033.0,
      "text": "What we found was this."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 37033.0,
      "end_time": 39006.0,
      "text": "Curly hair forms together in locks"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 39006.0,
      "end_time": 41232.0,
      "text": "that reshape themselves when you pull on them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 41232.0,
      "end_time": 42757.0,
      "text": "kind of like a spring."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 42757.0,
      "end_time": 44501.0,
      "text": "This was great news because springs"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 44501.0,
      "end_time": 46005.0,
      "text": "can be modeled mathematically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 46005.0,
      "end_time": 47508.0,
      "text": "meaning we can simulate their behavior"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 47508.0,
      "end_time": 49949.0,
      "text": "using a computer program."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 49949.0,
      "end_time": 51293.0,
      "text": "From the computer's perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 51293.0,
      "end_time": 53524.0,
      "text": "Merida's hair is just lots and lots of springs"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 53524.0,
      "end_time": 55765.0,
      "text": "that react to forces, such as gravity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 55765.0,
      "end_time": 57468.0,
      "text": "as Merida moves."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 57468.0,
      "end_time": 60023.0,
      "text": "The tests we ran using this approach were pretty good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 60023.0,
      "end_time": 61798.0,
      "text": "but not quite natural enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 61798.0,
      "end_time": 64484.0,
      "text": "While stiffer springs held the shape of the curl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 64483.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66553.0,
      "text": "it didn't bounce like natural curls."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 66553.0,
      "end_time": 68130.0,
      "text": "When we made the springs loser,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 68130.0,
      "end_time": 70498.0,
      "text": "her curls would unwind when she moved."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 70498.0,
      "end_time": 72245.0,
      "text": "This was even more obvious at high,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 72245.0,
      "end_time": 75245.0,
      "text": "often unrealistic speeds, found in animation."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 75245.0,
      "end_time": 76785.0,
      "text": "We realized we needed something"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 76785.0,
      "end_time": 78747.0,
      "text": "to preserve the structure of the curl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 78747.0,
      "end_time": 81508.0,
      "text": "but not impede the overall motion of the hair,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 81508.0,
      "end_time": 82988.0,
      "text": "kinda like digital hairspray."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 82988.0,
      "end_time": 85253.0,
      "text": "(can hissing) Oh, sorry (laughs)."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 85253.0,
      "end_time": 87241.0,
      "text": "We came up with the idea of connecting"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 87241.0,
      "end_time": 89763.0,
      "text": "the springs that make up Merida's on-screen hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 89763.0,
      "end_time": 92985.0,
      "text": "to invisible core springs like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 92985.0,
      "end_time": 94522.0,
      "text": "The core springs would limit the movement"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 94522.0,
      "end_time": 95555.0,
      "text": "of the on-screen hair"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 95555.0,
      "end_time": 97504.0,
      "text": "when the motion was more extreme."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 97504.0,
      "end_time": 99787.0,
      "text": "This way, we could have the best of both worlds."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 99787.0,
      "end_time": 101754.0,
      "text": "Our original simulation we create motion"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 101754.0,
      "end_time": 103480.0,
      "text": "that was soft and natural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 103480.0,
      "end_time": 105105.0,
      "text": "but the core springs would keep the curl"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 105105.0,
      "end_time": 107105.0,
      "text": "from unwinding too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 109001.0,
      "end_time": 111484.0,
      "text": "Figuring out how to make a hair simulation system"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 111484.0,
      "end_time": 113238.0,
      "text": "that could help us achieve the feeling we wanted"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 113238.0,
      "end_time": 114768.0,
      "text": "for Merida's hair was hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 114768.0,
      "end_time": 117039.0,
      "text": "It took a lot of iterations to get it right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 117039.0,
      "end_time": 118302.0,
      "text": "but it made a big difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 118302.0,
      "end_time": 121068.0,
      "text": "Merida feels like a real girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 121068.0,
      "end_time": 122818.0,
      "text": "messy, wild and free."
    }
  ]
}